snippet.textDisplay:
To all those comparing to NFAK, yes I understand if you think that way but you must realize that every singer has his unique style. Just because someone is a qawwal doesn't mean he's trying to follow NFAK. That's like saying every pop musician is like Michael Jackson. 
NFAK had a great vocal range but saying that this is why every other qawwal is inferior to him is a great injustice
